497
00:34:59,033 --> 00:35:01,831
Just get it off!

498
00:35:02,603 --> 00:35:04,537
Howard.

499
00:35:05,039 --> 00:35:07,872
Join us. We were just brainstorming.

500
00:35:08,609 --> 00:35:10,440
