- Yes.

501
00:35:10,611 --> 00:35:15,548
I was thinking it might be a good idea
to do a photo op at the build site...

502
00:35:15,716 --> 00:35:18,549
...where George would be in the...

503
00:35:19,119 --> 00:35:22,350
George in the foreground,
pointing up to the sky...

504
00:35:22,523 --> 00:35:24,115
...like this.
- Yes.

505
00:35:24,291 --> 00:35:29,285
Then I thought I could take my belt off,
as if to say, let's get to work!

506
00:35:29,463 --> 00:35:32,398
Right. Right-o.

507
00:35:32,967 --> 00:35:36,232
