515
00:35:55,322 --> 00:35:56,311
Folks?

516
00:35:56,657 --> 00:35:58,488
Excuse me.

517
00:35:59,193 --> 00:36:00,319
Hello.

518
00:36:00,494 --> 00:36:01,552
- Hi, honey.
- Hi, Daddy.

519
00:36:01,729 --> 00:36:03,526
- Is that a new coat? I like it.
- Thanks.

520
00:36:03,697 --> 00:36:08,361
