This offends me.

572
00:39:33,373 --> 00:39:35,466
Yeah, I'm sorry, Ton.

573
00:39:35,642 --> 00:39:36,939
I lost Lucy.

574
00:39:39,212 --> 00:39:42,875
I just think it's a shame because I've
come to rely on her for everything.

575
00:39:43,049 --> 00:39:47,213
And I trust her completely,
and she's funny.

576
00:39:47,387 --> 00:39:49,651
Not deliberately, of course.

577
00:39:49,822 --> 00:39:52,313
Hey, you know, it's probably
for the best though.

578
00:39:52,492 --> 00:39:54,790
Oh, yeah? Why is that?

579
00:39:55,495 --> 00:39:58,794
Two things I know is chess and women.

580
00:40:00,066 --> 00:40:04,901
Chess, it has rules, pieces,
rooks, knights, bishops.

581
00:40:05,071 --> 00:40:08,905
