Somebody wins, somebody loses.

582
00:40:09,075 --> 00:40:12,511
But women, they don't have no rules, man.

583
00:40:12,679 --> 00:40:14,840
They move in unpredictable ways too.

584
00:40:15,014 --> 00:40:17,505
