when it comes to women.

585
00:40:17,684 --> 00:40:21,017
You talk about your feelings
until your breath is sucked out your body.

586
00:40:22,021 --> 00:40:24,751
All men are pawns when it comes
to women.

587
00:40:24,924 --> 00:40:28,189
Especially a smart one like Lucy.
She's hard to control.

588
00:40:28,361 --> 00:40:31,819
And you know, the man has got
to be in control.

589
00:40:33,232 --> 00:40:34,756
Like with me.

590
00:40:34,934 --> 00:40:39,962
I come home. When I walk in,
I know my mama has dinner on the table.

591
00:40:41,441 --> 00:40:44,706
All right, so you're still living at home?

592
00:40:45,378 --> 00:40:47,369
Yeah. Yeah.

593
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:49,441
Of course.

594
00:40:54,053 --> 00:40:57,147
