668
00:45:04,203 --> 00:45:08,071
That is hard to say. I certainly would have
found it extremely erotic. Come back.

669
00:45:08,240 --> 00:45:10,140
I'm fine.

670
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:16,905
I don't know. Maybe I'm
just not good in bed.

671
00:45:17,149 --> 00:45:19,049
Maybe you're not.

672
00:45:21,387 --> 00:45:23,378
I am.

673
00:45:23,656 --> 00:45:27,319
- Yeah?
