00:46:21,380 --> 00:46:23,940
You're a really good listener.

687
00:46:27,052 --> 00:46:28,883
Luce?

688
00:46:29,555 --> 00:46:31,216
Luce?

689
00:46:31,890 --> 00:46:35,724
